{"tid":1591552,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"韓國瑜：當選總統可規劃太平島採石油 解決高雄財困","createTime":"2019-09-24T08:03:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-24T13:34:36.000Z","uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"561e7c1b7afe6c8a8a31d52a1e0486f7acd7cdef","tid":1591552,"uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T08:03:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.ctwant.com/article/8272\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ctwant.com%2Farticle%2F8272&d=CxVPqDM3fecqSGKEY7rAqGZ69rz5%2BYz%2FKt%2FQ7ZoV0Dw%3D&h=47c4f97f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ctwant.com/article/8272</a><br />\n<br />\n國民黨總統參選人韓國瑜，去年在參選高雄市長期間，曾提及欲在太平島開採石油議題，但近日卻否認此政見，韓國瑜競選辦公室發言人何庭歡24日受訪時表示，若韓明年當選總統就可努力規劃。<br />\n<br />\n何庭歡24日受訪時被問到，太平島開採石油議題是否會寫在韓的競選政策白皮書上，她未正面回應但強調，韓在競選高雄市長時的政見也未寫到，且開發石油是屬中央職權，若韓明年當選總統，就可以努力規畫中油前往當地探勘石油計畫，而太平島隸屬於高雄市，假設真的有開發，高雄市政府也可分一杯羹，解決龐大的負債。"},{"pid":"3bdde1888c3e9585bd76c7ba9c5d258f9837ac49","tid":1591552,"uid":997,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T08:04:42.000Z","msg":"on9,油價依家都唔值錢<br />\n又黎發大財 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e259b3d3d36d1ee8a103074f4b562b06202e364b","tid":1591552,"uid":260085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T08:05:15.000Z","msg":"發大財畫大餅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86fca6d458bb37c10c3f9a705e985863973cb148","tid":1591552,"uid":51720,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T08:07:07.000Z","msg":"強國：太平島屬於南海主權一部分 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9545528c16c3193a7e0955cbde4422b28689ff6","tid":1591552,"uid":109780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T08:08:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92362061d8eed2bb4700f1a9e94b3acb0c74351a","tid":1591552,"uid":25468,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"c